<div class="page-hero"><p class="page-hero__label">Adopting from us</p><h1 class="page-hero__title">The <em style="font-style:italic;color:var(--or)">adoption process</em></h1><p class="page-hero__desc">Transparent and rigorous — because every adoption is a decision for the next 12 to 16 years.</p></div>
<section class="section"><div class="container"><div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:5rem;align-items:start" class="reveal">
  <div>
    <p class="section__label">The steps</p>
    <h2 class="section__title" style="margin-bottom:2.5rem">From first contact<br>to your new companion</h2>
    <div class="adoption-steps">
      <div class="adoption-step"><div class="adoption-step__num">1</div><div class="adoption-step__content"><h3>First contact</h3><p>Fill in the contact form specifying the breed you're interested in, your family situation, and your expectations. We reply within 24 hours.</p></div></div>
      <div class="adoption-step"><div class="adoption-step__num">2</div><div class="adoption-step__content"><h3>Phone conversation</h3><p>A 15–20 minute call to get to know you better — your home, your lifestyle, your experience with dogs. No judgement, just honesty.</p></div></div>
      <div class="adoption-step"><div class="adoption-step__num">3</div><div class="adoption-step__content"><h3>Visit to the kennel</h3><p>Mandatory before any reservation. You meet the parents, you observe the puppies, you ask all your questions. This is also the moment where you "choose" your puppy — or it chooses you.</p></div></div>
      <div class="adoption-step"><div class="adoption-step__num">4</div><div class="adoption-step__content"><h3>Reservation & deposit</h3><p>A CHF 500 deposit confirms your reservation. The puppy is then reserved in your name. We send photos and updates regularly until departure.</p></div></div>
      <div class="adoption-step"><div class="adoption-step__num">5</div><div class="adoption-step__content"><h3>The big day</h3><p>At minimum 8 weeks, your puppy leaves with health record, pedigree, microchip, welcome kit and adoption contract. We remain available on WhatsApp for the first year.</p></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div>
    <p class="section__label">Our requirements</p>
    <h2 class="section__title" style="margin-bottom:2rem">What we ask of you</h2>
    <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1rem">
      <div style="padding:1.5rem;border:1px solid var(--gris-clair);border-radius:var(--radius)"><h3 style="font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:.6rem">🏠 A stable home</h3><p style="font-size:.88rem;color:var(--gris);line-height:1.7">Flat or house, owner or tenant with landlord approval. No minimum surface area — but a firm commitment to daily exercise.</p></div>
      <div style="padding:1.5rem;border:1px solid var(--gris-clair);border-radius:var(--radius)"><h3 style="font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:.6rem">⏰ Available time</h3><p style="font-size:.88rem;color:var(--gris);line-height:1.7">A puppy cannot be left alone for more than 4 hours in the first months. If you work full time, plan ahead (pet-sitter, trusted neighbour, partial remote working).</p></div>
      <div style="padding:1.5rem;border:1px solid var(--gris-clair);border-radius:var(--radius)"><h3 style="font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:.6rem">💰 Realistic budget</h3><p style="font-size:.88rem;color:var(--gris);line-height:1.7">Beyond the purchase price: vet (CHF 300–600/year), food (CHF 600–1,200/year), recommended health insurance (CHF 30–80/month), grooming (Pomsky: CHF 80–120/session).</p></div>
      <div style="margin-top:1rem;background:var(--noir);color:var(--blanc);padding:2rem;border-radius:var(--radius)"><h3 style="font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:300;margin-bottom:.8rem">Our guarantee</h3><p style="font-size:.88rem;color:rgba(248,246,241,.7);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:1.2rem">2-year genetic guarantee on hereditary diseases certified by our tests. In case of confirmed diagnosis by a vet, we refund or exchange — your choice.</p><p style="font-size:.78rem;color:var(--or);letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase">Full terms in the adoption contract</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div></div></section>
